snippet.textDisplay: Pakistan ka music sunke lagta hai gale laga loon apne Pakistani Bhai behnon ko. Kaash ye sarhadein na bani hoti aur hum sab ek saath hote pehle ki tarah ek hi desh banke ❤️. Bharat to apna culture bhool chuka hai, yahan ke gaanon mein to west ghus gaya hai but Pakistani music mein abhi bhi purana Bharat saaf dikhta hai. Shukar hai dono Bhaiyon mein se ek ne to culture pakad rakha hai abhi bhi. Isiliye Bharat mein zyadatar log Pakistani music hi sunte Hain aur Pakistani serials hi dekhta Hain.
